<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="man-n">man <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /mæn/    美 /mæn/  </p>
<p>(pl men)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(成年) 男子；男子汉：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Come on, <strong>be a man</strong> now. No more crying. 
好啦，做个男子汉，不要再哭了。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>(不论性别的) 人：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Any man could do it. 
这事儿任何人都能做。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>人类：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Man has caused much damage to the environment.
人类已对环境造成了很大的破坏。</p></div></div>